high_descs: Turn around, head to the fridge, turn left and turn left again toward the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn left and go around the table.
Cut the potato on the table.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick it back up.
Go left and turn to right toward the trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the fridge on your left. Turn left and walk to the black table on your left.
Pick up a knife from the table.
Turn left and stop at the potato placed on the table.
Cut the potato into slices.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the knife in the fridge. Close the fridge door.
Turn left and go to the black table.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Turn right and head to the fridge. Open the fridge door.
Put the potato slice in the fridge and close the door. Wait for ten minutes, take out the potato slice and close the fridge door.
Turn left and reach the trash can on your right.
Put the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a refrigerated potato slice into a trash can.
